{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 57,
  "title": "第五十七章（淳風）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "以正治國，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以奇用兵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以無事取天下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾何以知其然哉，以此。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天下多忌諱而民彌貧。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民多利器，國家滋昏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人多伎巧，奇物滋起。"
    },
    {
      "text": "法物滋彰，盜賊多有。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故聖人云："
    },
    {
      "text": "我無為而民自化，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我好靜而民自正，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我無事而民自富，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我無欲而民自朴。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以，至也。天使正身之人，使有國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奇，詐也。天使詐偽之人，使用兵也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以無事無為之人，使取天下為之主。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此，今也。老子言，我何以知天意然哉，以今日所見知。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下謂人主也。忌諱者防禁也。今煩則姦生，禁多則下詐，相殆故貧。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器者，權也。 民多權則視者眩於目，聽者惑於耳，上下不親，故國家昏亂。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人謂人君、百里諸侯也。多技巧，謂刻畫宮觀，雕琢章服，奇物滋起，下則化上，飾金鏤玉，文繡彩色日以滋甚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "法物，好物也。珍好之物滋生彰著，則農事廢， 飢寒並至，而盜賊多有也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂下事也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人言：我修道承天，無所改作，而民自化成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人言：我好靜，不言不教，而民自忠正也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我無徭役徵召之事，民安其業故皆自富也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我常無欲，去華文，微服飾，民則隨我為質樸也。 聖人言：我修道守真，絕去六情，民自隨我而清也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
